timeForSettle.title: Timer for Settling
timeForSettle.description: How long an object must sit still until a succesful settled object is registered

settledColor.title: Settled Color
settledColor.description: The color of the physics object after the object has settled

notSettledColor.title: Not Settled Color
notSettledColor.description: The color of the physics object before the object has settled

autoRender.title: Auto Render
autoRender.description: Disable to only render when camera is moving (saves power when the camera is still)

distanceMax.title: Distance Max
distanceMax.description: Setting this at 0 will give an infinite distance limit

inertiaFactor.title: Inertia Factor
inertiaFactor.description: Higher value means that the camera will continue moving after the user has stopped dragging. 0 is fully responsive.

focusEntity.title: Focus Entity
focusEntity.description: Entity for the camera to focus on. If blank, then the camera will use the whole scene

frameOnStart.title: Frame on Start
frameOnStart.description: Frames the entity or scene at the start of the application."

orbitSensitivity.title: Orbit Sensitivity
orbitSensitivity.description: How fast the camera moves around the orbit. Higher is faster

distanceSensitivity.title: Distance Sensitivity
distanceSensitivity.description: How fast the camera moves in and out. Higher is faster

orbitSensitivity.title: Orbit Sensitivity
orbitSensitivity.description: How fast the camera moves around the orbit. Higher is faster

distanceSensitivity.title: Distance Sensitivity
distanceSensitivity.description: How fast the camera moves in and out. Higher is faster

dropButtonTimerThreshold.title: Drop Button Timer Threshold
dropButtonTimerThreshold.description: How long the button can be held down before a drop will not occur. In seconds

dropMoveThreshold.title: Drop Button Distance Moved Threshold
dropMoveThreshold.description: How far can the user move their finger while trying to drop before a drop will not occur

fanSpeed.title: Fan Rotation Speed
fanSpeed.description: How quickly the blades of the fan will rotate

moveSpeed.title: Screen Movement Speed
moveSpeed.description: How quickly the screen will approach the correct point. Higher number is slower

heightOffset.title: Screen Height Offset
heightOffset.description: Height Offset from tracking the cube dropper

targetEntity.title: Focus Entity
targetEntity.description: Entity for the camera to focus on. If blank, then the camera will use the whole scene

moveSpeed.title: Follow Speed
moveSpeed.description: How quickly the screen will approach the correct point. Higher number is slower

scanLineSpeed.title: Scan Line Speed
scanLineSpeed.description: How quickly the scan lines will pan across the screens display

oneWaveTime.title: Time for wave
oneWaveTime.description: Time for one wave of the flag

maxWaveTimeDelta.title: Max Wave Time +- Delta
maxWaveTimeDelta.description: Max Time added or subtracted from the base time

zRot1.title: Initial Z Rotation
zRot1.description: Starting point for the flags rotation

zRot2.title: Ending Z Rotation
zRot2.description: Ending point for the flags rotation
